        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double"><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Strength</font></b></td>
          <td style="border-bottom: 1px double" colspan="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Makes 
            you hit more often for maximum damage. Weight allowance is directly 
            tied to your strength.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double"><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Dexterity</font></b></td>
          <td style="border-bottom: 1px double" colspan="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Increases 
            the ability to hit and increases your chance to regain casting when 
            hit or interrupted.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double"><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Agility</font></b></td>
          <td style="border-bottom: 1px double" colspan="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Helps 
            dodging and improves AC. </font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double"><b><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Charisma</font></b></td>
          <td style="border-bottom: 1px double" colspan="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Helps 
            overcome resistance when "effect" style spells such as debuffs or 
            charms are used on a critter. Also improves faction with NPCs and 
            helps improve prices with vendors.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double"><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Stamina</font></b></td>
          <td style="border-bottom: 1px double" colspan="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Gives 
            a few extra HP per level. Also allows you to fight longer and swim 
            longer without getting tired.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double"><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Intelligence</font></b></td>
          <td style="border-bottom: 1px double" colspan="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Determines 
            mana store for wizards and improves the rate of advancing your skills.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
