        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><b>Evocation</b></td>
          <td width="38%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1">1</td>
          <td width="41%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><font face="Arial">Direct 
            damage spells. Also see the <a href="../spells/default.htm">spell 
            list</a></font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><b>Channeling</b></td>
          <td width="38%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1">4</td>
          <td width="41%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><font face="Arial">Increases 
            chances not to be disrupted while casting, even when hit. Eventually 
            you can even run while casting certain spells.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><b>Meditate</b></td>
          <td width="38%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1">4</td>
          <td width="41%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><font face="Arial">Allows 
            you to regain mana faster, and increase the speed of memorizing and 
            scribing. You must put 1 practice point into this before it will start 
            going up on its own.</font></td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><b>Specialization</b></td>
          <td width="38%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1">20</td>
          <td width="41%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"> 
            <p><font face="Arial">Allows you to specialize a categry of magic 
              in type of magic which means less mana usage and faster casting 
              spells.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial">You can specialize all categories to 50, but 
              only one above.</font></p>
          </td>
