        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><b>Bind 
            Wounds</b></td>
          <td width="38%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1">1</td>
          <td width="41%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"> 
            <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Using bandages, 
              you can heal an amount of damage that increases with your skill. 
              You must be below 50% health for <b>Bind Wounds</b> to work.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Skill capacity</b>: 
              (lvl x 4) + 4 (100 may be max)</font></p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top"> 
          <td width="21%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"><b>Dodge</b></td>
          <td width="38%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1">22</td>
          <td width="41%" style="border-bottom: 1px double" class="unnamed1"> 
            <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Increses the 
              liklihood that you will avoid an attack altogether.</font></p>
